CGI (Common Gateway Interface) conjunto de estandares para intercambiar info entre servidores web y scripts en c++.

Mi apache
ScriptAlias /cgi-bin/ /var/www/cgi-bin/
<Directory "/var/www/cgi-bin/">
        AllowOverride all
        Options +ExecCGI -MultiViews +SymLinksIfOwnerMatch
        Require all granted
        Allow from all
</Directory>




DEMO
<Directory "/var/www/cgi-bin">
   AllowOverride None
   Options ExecCGI
   Order allow,deny
   Allow from all
</Directory>
 
<Directory "/var/www/cgi-bin">
Options All
</Directory>

